query.result:
143 Pistoia before the Blacks becomes thin;  
144 then Florence renews people and customs.  

145 Mars draws vapor of Val di Magra  
146 which is wrapped in turbid clouds;  
147 and with impetuous and fierce storm  

148 over Campo Picen will be fought;  
149 where it suddenly will break the fog,  
150 so that every White will be wounded there.
